subtasks.description:
For Step 5, check if at least one of the following groups of documents exists (the condition is satisfied if any one of the groups is fully present):
Group 1: All of Tax Form 1040 for {computed_application_year}-1 and {computed_application_year}-2, Tax Form 1065 for {computed_application_year}-1 and {computed_application_year}-2, and Tax Form 1065SCHK1 for {computed_application_year}-1 and {computed_application_year}-2;
Group 2: All of Tax Form 1040 for {computed_application_year}-2 and {computed_application_year}-3, Tax Form 1065 for {computed_application_year}-2 and {computed_application_year}-3, and Tax Form 1065SCHK1 for {computed_application_year}-2 and {computed_application_year}-3;
Group 3: All of Tax Form 1040, Tax Form 1065, and Tax Form 1065SCHK1 for {computed_application_year}-1;
Group 4: All of Tax Form 1040, Tax Form 1065, and Tax Form 1065SCHK1 for {computed_application_year}-2.
If any group is complete, log the passed result message and terminate the process. Otherwise, raise the discrepancy message.
